text = "THE BIG ONE

A humongous 72 by 48 Minesweeper grid with hundreds of mines! How fast can you complete it?

You start with 0 Minecoins and earn them as you play. You get to keep all the minecoins you collect if you win, but you'll only get a percentage of them if you lose.

Select one of the 9 difficulties below and press the button to start the challenge."
label_settings = SubResource("LabelSettings_8f808")
horizontal_alignment = 1
vertical_alignment = 1
autowrap_mode = 2

